{
  "stem": "20084.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the-- the guy in charge of the Plaszow was a guy by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Getz. ?] He was a big fellow, a handsome fellow, maybe 6'2', maybe weighed 220, maybe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Big fellow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was riding, always, on a white horse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had a couple of dogs hanging-- having around him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was like, going hunting for ducks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He used to shoot people just-- just-- just like this, just for-- like a-- like hunting for ducks, like they do in this country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was very, very sadistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very sadistic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once-- one incident he was-- we were working in Plaszow, up on the road, cleaning, cleaning something, a road, or moving mountains from one side the mountain.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The next day, the mountain was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Just doing-- thousands of people were doing with shovels, with picks, with-- with-- with-- just moving one mountain to the other side, just to keep us working.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one of his dogs bit my brother, Sam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Grabbed him here, grabbed him here by the ribs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He still has, today, the-- the marks from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was just lucky because nobody survived him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few more minutes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, so-- and this was-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I don't remember, I know it was hot and summer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Must have been the end of June, the beginning of August, when they started bringing in the trains assembling the cattle trains, for us to ship us out to different destination.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
